Introduction to New Mountain Vantage

New Mountain Vantage

Focused on concentrated positions with opportunities to build significant shareholder value through improvement in
operations, capital allocation, and governance

Leverages the experience, strength and skills of New Mountain Capital's leading private equity franchise

Vantage has assembled a team of advisers dedicated to the NFG effort:

